{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 \b \fs36 Odd saturation\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 Two waveshping saturation styles using sin() functions, feturing {\i odd harmonics}. *Wavy Top, no discontinueties but may fold the wavefom over a bit at some settings. *Flat Top, waveform flatens off at 0dB. Can be used to add vibe or as a maximiser.\par}
}

