{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 \b \fs36 Smooth Clipper\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 Waveshaper that gets much more distorted near -1dB, but never reaches a perfectly flat top. Hard clipper at the output to prevent levels over 0dB. Can be used to add vibe or as a maximiser.\par}
}

